<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Second, Binance enforces geographic restrictions based on regulatory requirements. Residents of certain countries cannot take part at all, while others face partial restrictions. For example:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Users in Singapore, Nigeria, Israel, and Hong Kong are disqualified entirely from joining as referrers or invitees.</span></li>
