</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Third, Binance actively investigates fraudulent activity. Some users try bulk registrations with so-called </span><b>binance free money code</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> tricks, but Binance bans this behavior. The company also clarified that rebate vouchers earned through Referral Mode cannot be applied to API trading after September 2024.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Finally, Binance reserves the right to interpret or modify the program at its discretion. All participants must comply with the Binance Terms of Use and the referral program’s own rules. Any breach of these terms, whether deliberate or accidental, may result in loss of rewards and removal from the program.</span></p>
