<h3 class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Step 1: Sign Up With the Code</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Start by creating your Binance account. This is where you enter the Binance referral code VB2025 so the bonus is linked.</p>
