<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">What to Do if the Binance Referral Code Doesn’t Work?</span></h2>
<p>Most failures come down to mistyping the code, entering it after signup, or being in a restricted region. The code can&#8217;t be added or changed once the account exists, so double-check it before hitting Create Account. Here&#8217;s what usually causes it:</p>
