<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Fees drop if you trade a lot or hold Binance Coin (BNB). Binance has a VIP system where each level comes with lower maker/taker fees. The requirements are tied to your 30-day trading volume plus how much BNB you hold.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You also get a 25% discount if you pay fees with BNB. On top of that, Binance sometimes runs promos or referral offers that knock fees down even more.</span></p>
